HEADWORD: Suspender
<hw>Sus*pend"er</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>One who, or that
which, suspends; esp., one of a pair of straps or braces worn over the
shoulders, for holding up the trousers.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

